title: Ceph Storage: OSD - BlueFS Write-Ahead Log
agents: linux
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the usage of the Write-Ahead Log of the BlueFS of an Object Storage Daemon in a Ceph cluster.
 
 The usage is checked against values configurable using the ruleset "Filesystems (used space and growth)".

item:
 The OSDs ID.

discovery:
 One service is created for each OSD.
